# ============================================
# AI REVIEW BOT
# --------------------------------------------
# This project analyzes documents and provides:
# - Clarity prediction (ML Model)
# - Score prediction (Regression Model)
# - Rule-based issue detection
# - Bilingual output (English + Tamil)
# - Automatic dataset generation & training
# ============================================




# ============================================
# LOAD DATASET
# --------------------------------------------
# Reads dataset containing:
# text     → document content
# clarity  → label (good / medium / poor)
# score    → rating (1–10)
# ============================================

# ============================================
# TEXT PREPROCESSING
# --------------------------------------------
# Converts text to lowercase
# Removes special characters
# Helps ML model understand patterns better
# ============================================



# ============================================
# FEATURE ENGINEERING
# --------------------------------------------
# Extracts additional useful features:
# - Length of text
# - Presence of introduction
# - Presence of conclusion
# Improves model accuracy
# ============================================



# ============================================
# TEXT VECTORIZATION (TF-IDF)
# --------------------------------------------
# Converts text into numerical format
# So machine learning model can process it
# ============================================



# ============================================
# LABEL ENCODING
# --------------------------------------------
# Converts clarity labels (good/medium/poor)
# into numeric values for model training
# ============================================




# ============================================
# DATA SPLITTING
# --------------------------------------------
# Splits data into:
# - Training data (for learning)
# - Testing data (for evaluation)
# ============================================


# ============================================
# MODEL TRAINING
# --------------------------------------------
# RandomForestClassifier → predicts clarity
# RandomForestRegressor → predicts score
# ============================================



# ============================================
# MODEL EVALUATION
# --------------------------------------------
# Accuracy → classification performance
# MSE → regression error
# ============================================


# ============================================
# MODEL SAVING
# --------------------------------------------
# Saves trained models using pickle
# So they can be reused without retraining
# ============================================



# ============================================
# LANGUAGE DETECTION
# --------------------------------------------
# Detects if input is Tamil or English
# Based on Unicode character range
# ============================================


# ============================================
# RULE-BASED VALIDATION
# --------------------------------------------
# Checks document quality:
# - Introduction presence
# - Conclusion presence
# - Content length
# - Sentence structure
# - Repetition
# - Capitalization
# ============================================




# ============================================
# SCORE ADJUSTMENT
# --------------------------------------------
# Adjusts ML predicted score based on:
# - Clarity level
# - Identified issues
# Makes output more realistic
# ============================================



# ============================================
# FEEDBACK GENERATION
# --------------------------------------------
# Generates meaningful feedback based on:
# - Clarity
# - Score
# - Issues
# ============================================



# ============================================
# TRANSLATION (ENGLISH → TAMIL)
# --------------------------------------------
# Uses GoogleTranslator
# Converts output into Tamil language
# ============================================



# ============================================
# FINAL OUTPUT GENERATION
# --------------------------------------------
# Combines:
# - Language detection
# - English output
# - Tamil output
# Returns structured response
# ============================================


# ============================================
# FLASK API SERVER
# --------------------------------------------
# Handles client requests
# Provides endpoint for document review
# ============================================




# ============================================
# /review API
# --------------------------------------------
# Accepts text input
# Sends to ML model
# Returns structured output
# ============================================


# ============================================
# AUTO TRAINING PIPELINE
# --------------------------------------------
# Automatically:
# - Generates dataset
# - Trains model
# - Saves models
# ============================================
